To login once on the system use the following script,

	#!/bin/sh

	# Set user login
		LOGIN="chilli"

	# Login LOGIN
		login $LOGIN

To login using SSH,

	#!/bin/sh

	# Set user login
		LOGIN="chilli"

	# Set IP target
		IPSSH="10.11.200.150"

	# Starting SSH session
		ssh $LOGIN@$IPSSH

To log using graphic session, please refer to your GUI documentation (Cnammon, GNOME...) and distribution doc.
